<div class="location-info-panel">
  <h3>Current Location</h3>

  <div class="location-description">
    <% if zone.biome == "city" %>
      <p>You are standing in the bustling streets of <strong><%= zone.name %></strong>.
         Merchants call out their wares, guards patrol the cobblestone roads, and
         adventurers gather to share tales of their exploits.</p>
      <p class="location-hint">ğŸ’¡ You can visit shops, talk to NPCs, or exit to the wilderness.</p>
    <% elsif zone.biome == "plains" %>
      <p>The open <strong><%= zone.name %></strong> stretch before you. Tall grass sways
         in the breeze, and the road leads to distant settlements.</p>
      <p class="location-hint">âš ï¸ Wild creatures may attack travelers here.</p>
    <% elsif zone.biome == "forest" %>
      <p>Dense trees surround you in the <strong><%= zone.name %></strong>. Sunlight
         filters through the canopy, and you can hear wildlife moving in the underbrush.</p>
      <p class="location-hint">ğŸŒ¿ Herbs and wood can be gathered here.</p>
    <% else %>
      <p>You are at <strong><%= zone.name %></strong> [<%= position.x %>, <%= position.y %>].</p>
    <% end %>
  </div>

  <% if tile.respond_to?(:metadata) && tile.metadata.present? %>
    <div class="tile-features">
      <% if tile.metadata["npc"] %>
        <div class="feature-item">
          <span class="feature-icon">ğŸ‘¤</span>
          <span><%= tile.metadata["npc"] %></span>
        </div>
      <% end %>
      <% if tile.metadata["shop"] %>
        <div class="feature-item">
          <span class="feature-icon">ğŸª</span>
          <span><%= tile.metadata["shop"] %></span>
        </div>
      <% end %>
      <% if tile.metadata["dungeon"] %>
        <div class="feature-item feature-item--danger">
          <span class="feature-icon">âš”ï¸</span>
          <span>Dungeon Entrance: <%= tile.metadata["dungeon"] %></span>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  <% end %>
</div>

